   - TRIM() on a non-text/varchar column → add ::text cast: TRIM("col"::text)
   - WHERE col <> '' or col != '' on integer/bigint/numeric → change to col IS NOT NULL
   - WHERE col = '' on integer/bigint/numeric → change to col IS NULL
   - Numeric aggregations on text columns → wrap: NULLIF(TRIM(REPLACE("col"::text, ',', '')), '')::numeric
   - Use COALESCE for nullable JOIN columns
